Content: Just catching up on the chat. Please note that the whitepaper out there is old and the PoP protocol has evolved since then. VeriBlock uses a form of block reference braiding mixed with finality delay parameters that make any privately-mined chain have to perform PoP publications which give full visibility of the chain (where the attack starts, proof the attack is being produced at a sufficient difficulty, whether the attack is still possible).
